OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some sunshine. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Fvariable amounts of cloud and clear
OL,9,Fspells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FDry with some sunshine,
OL,12,Fperhaps some low cloud around the
OL,13,FShetland coast. Quite warm across
OL,14,Fwestern parts of Orkney.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,17,Fon Friday with some showery rain.
OL,18,FOutbreaks of rain spreading east
OL,19,Fduring Saturday and Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
